    <style>
        /* Base reference for internal calculation: 16px = 1rem */
        html {
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        /* Essential for Footer-Push Logic */ 
        html, body { 
            height: 100%; margin: 0; padding: 0;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; 
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* This container grows to fill empty space, pushing the footer down */
        .content-container {
            flex: 1 0 auto; 
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            /* Padding is handled by .content-container in styles.css (1.25rem) */
        }

        footer {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        /* Ensure the overlay covers the full viewport precisely */
        #navOverlay {
            display: none; 
            position: fixed; 
            top: 0; 
            left: 0; 
            width: 100%; 
            height: 100%; 
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); 
            z-index: 8500;
        }
    </style>

            <style>

                .editable { position: relative; min-height: 1.2em; cursor: pointer; box-sizing: border-box; width: 100%; outline: none; display: block !important; clear: both; }

                h2, h3, p { display: block !important; margin: 0 0 0.9375rem 0; padding-bottom: 0.625rem; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; }
                .editable:empty::before { content: attr(data-placeholder); color: #888; opacity: 0.6; pointer-events: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important; }
                .block_container { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; width: 100%; min-height: 2rem; }
                .block_spacer { height: 2.5rem; width: 100%; }
                .resize-handle { width: 2.75rem; height: 2.75rem; position: absolute; right: -0.125rem; bottom: -0.125rem; cursor: nwse-resize; z-index: 9999; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #ebd5c9; }
                .resize-handle::before { content: "\f337"; font-family: "Font Awesome 6 Free"; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.75rem; }

<script>
    // Logic remains in JS but controls elements sized by REM in CSS
    function toggleNav(e) {
        if(e) e.stopPropagation();
        const nav = document.getElementById('nav-sidebar');
        const hamburger = document.getElementById('headerHamburger');
        
        const isOpen = nav.classList.toggle('open');
        hamburger.classList.toggle('active');
        
        document.getElementById('navOverlay').style.display = isOpen ? 'block' : 'none';
        
        // Locking the body scroll for a better mobile experience
        document.body.style.overflow = isOpen ? 'hidden' : 'auto';
    }

    function toggleDropdown(btn) {
        btn.classList.toggle('active');
        btn.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('show');
    }
</script>
